{"tid":1562631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無打算商場唱美國國歌？","createTime":"2019-09-12T05:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:56:58.000Z","uid":273719,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2230dfca704234c8366a40035b840117c1f0305b","tid":1562631,"uid":273719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"幾日唱歌po多過行動po，有無步雨傘後塵感覺？<br />\n依排有種自我沉溺嘅味道，沉醉快樂抗爭<br />\n對政府無壓力，中共無批評<br />\n我認為中共有批評嘅事情代表香港人做對了，但宜家中共無出聲，各地産商嘅大型商場又默許集會。<br />\n<br />\n令到香港人以為抗爭十分成功，開始自大起嚟，此情況好易俾人食住上。<br />\n<br />\n但如果轉換唱美國國歌<br />\n1: 美國人關注<br />\n2: 掌摑共産黨副嘴臉<br />\n3: 我地美國戰線相當重要 唱美國國歌 話俾美國人知我地渴望 pass HK Human Right and Democracy Act<br />\n4: 美國國歌有勇武振奮人心效果<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"4bb43f67677cbd44d1f82f700f1aeaf816e61e76","tid":1562631,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f6d37dac9d7587779edc8fb465b2d309e94e6d0a","tid":1562631,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔唱美國國歌<br />\n要唱唱返我地自己個首"},{"pid":"7e6275aef94929970e6e113ffaaa08a83c148daf","tid":1562631,"uid":265066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:42:57.000Z","msg":"